### Security Model

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Security Layers                       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 1: Connection Authentication                       │
│   - Local-only binding (127.0.0.1)                      │
│   - Token-based auth (generated on server start)        │
│   - Origin validation (only Neuman Brain domain)        │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 2: Command Filtering (Optional)                    │
│   - Allowlist mode: Only approved commands              │
│   - Blocklist mode: Block dangerous commands            │
│   - Confirmation prompts for destructive operations     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 3: Directory Sandboxing (Optional)                 │
│   - Restrict to specific directories                    │
│   - User configures "workspace" directories             │
│   - Prevent access to system directories                │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 4: User Consent                                    │
│   - Clear warnings about local execution                │
│   - "Power User Mode" opt-in                            │
│   - Audit log of all executed commands                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

