## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|
| Security vulnerabilities | HIGH | Local-only binding, auth tokens, sandboxing |
| Complex user setup | MEDIUM | One-click installers, clear docs, setup wizard |
| Cross-platform bugs | MEDIUM | Extensive testing matrix, CI/CD for all platforms |
| Browser limitations | LOW | Companion server bypasses browser sandbox |
| Maintenance burden | MEDIUM | Use proven libraries (node-pty), minimal custom code |

